<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:17:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>情报官员表示，外国影响力参与者将适应美国总统竞选的变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/foreign-influence-actors-adapt-us-presidential-race-changes-says-intelligence-2024-07-29/</link><description>一名美国情报官员周一表示，针对 11 月大选进行影响力行动的美国敌人预计将适应总统竞选的发展，这显然是指乔·拜登放弃连任竞选。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/foreign-influence-actors-adapt-us-presidential-race-changes-says-intelligence-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>独家：SpaceX 正在洽谈在澳大利亚海岸着陆并回收星舰火箭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-talks-land-recover-starship-rocket-off-australias-coast-2024-07-29/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，SpaceX 正在与美国和澳大利亚官员进行谈判，以在澳大利亚海岸着陆并回收其一艘 Starship 火箭，这可能是埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的公司在该地区扩大业务的第一步，因为两国加强了安全关系。与计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/spacex-talks-land-recover-starship-rocket-off-australias-coast-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>被控充当中国特工的美国公民开始受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/trial-begins-us-citizen-accused-acting-chinese-agent-2024-07-29/</link><description>中国一名前大学教授周一在布鲁克林受审，罪名是他作为中国特工，在中国情报官员的指导下监视反对北京共产党政府的美国活动人士。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:44:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/trial-begins-us-citizen-accused-acting-chinese-agent-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称乌克兰援助计划价值高达2亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-aid-package-valued-up-200-million-white-house-says-2024-07-29/</link><description>白宫国家安全发言人约翰·柯比表示，美国周一宣布了一项针对乌克兰的新安全援助计划，价值高达 2 亿美元，其中包括防空系统和反坦克武器。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/ukraine-aid-package-valued-up-200-million-white-house-says-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平和意大利总理梅洛尼在北京会面讨论冲突</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-calls-balanced-eu-china-trade-xi-meeting-2024-07-29/</link><description>梅洛尼办公室称，中国国家主席习近平和意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周一在北京举行会议，讨论了乌克兰战争和中东危机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-calls-balanced-eu-china-trade-xi-meeting-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>乒乓球-朝鲜晋级混双决赛挑战中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-fan-chen-cruise-past-first-round-paris-2024-07-29/</link><description>朝鲜神秘的混双队击败香港队，晋级决赛，与强大的中国队一决高下，八年来首次获得奥运会奖牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/table-tennis-chinas-fan-chen-cruise-past-first-round-paris-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示全球经济增长弹性与降息预期不符</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economys-growing-resilience-odds-with-rate-cut-expectations-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透社调查的数百名经济学家对今年和明年全球增长前景的乐观情绪正在增强，尽管他们坚持降息预测，但风险仍然倾向于通胀上升。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economys-growing-resilience-odds-with-rate-cut-expectations-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳全球销售额三年多来首次下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-posts-surprise-drop-quarterly-global-sales-spending-slows-2024-07-29/</link><description>麦当劳周一报告称，其全球销售额意外下降，这是 13 个季度以来的首次下降，原因是寻求优惠的消费者避开了包括巨无霸在内的价格较高的菜单项。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-posts-surprise-drop-quarterly-global-sales-spending-slows-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>羽毛球-中国队巴黎连胜被马来西亚人和丹麦人终结</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-malaysia-ends-chinas-paris-winning-streak-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，中国队在巴黎奥运会上遭遇羽毛球首场失利，混双热门选手冯彦哲和黄东萍不敌马来西亚组合，而中国男双队则被丹麦队击败。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:37:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-malaysia-ends-chinas-paris-winning-streak-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：比较平静，但能持续多久？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-29/</link><description>欧洲、中东和非洲地区财经与市场突发新闻记者 Alun John 对美国和全球市场的未来展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:21:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>跳水-杨连杰让中国横扫梦想继续走上正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-yang-lian-win-mens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，杨浩和连俊杰在男子双人10米跳台比赛中表现出色，为中国队包揽全部八块跳水金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/diving-chinas-yang-lian-win-mens-synchronised-10m-platform-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国名将盛在巴黎夺得第二枚射击金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-south-korean-ban-wins-womens-10-metre-air-rifle-gold-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一，中国选手盛立浩在沙托鲁射击中心表现出色，夺得男子10米气步枪比赛的第二枚巴黎奥运会金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:16:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/shooting-south-korean-ban-wins-womens-10-metre-air-rifle-gold-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>香港维权人士擅自带出监狱投诉表格被定罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一判定民主活动人士周文豪和他的律师胡菲丽丝去年未经授权将一份供监察员使用的投诉表格带出监狱。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-activist-convicted-taking-complaint-form-out-prison-without-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>中国谴责美日在海上问题和军事扩张问题上的“不实指控”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</link><description>中国外交部周一表示，美国和日本之间的联合声明在海上问题上“错误地指责”中国，并指责中国正常的军事发展和国防政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rebukes-us-japan-false-accusations-maritime-issues-military-expansion-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国7月份制造业活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</link><description>路透周一的一项民意调查显示，中国7月份工厂活动可能连续第三个月萎缩，由于旷日持久的房地产危机和就业不稳定拖累经济增长，官员们需要推出进一步刺激措施的预期依然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-manufacturing-activity-seen-extending-decline-july-2024-07-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>